<h1>NANOGrav Search for Gravitational Waves</h1>  

<p>

The NANOGrav (North American Nanohertz Observatory for Gravitational
Waves) consortium is timing an array of very stable millisecond
pulsars to try to detect gravitational waves.  NANOGrav in turn is
part of the larger International Pulsar Timing Array (IPTA)
consortium.

